Abuja – The Port Harcourt First Daughter, Tacha has been criticized severally for allegedly bleaching her skin. Big Brother Naija housemate, Tacha’s knuckles and face has got a lot of celebrities and some Nigerians talking. The video recording was made by fans of the ongoing reality show and the 23-year old Instagram influencer has been getting some bashing for it. Many have likened her knuckles to the colours of a roasted plantain. Throwback pictures have shown that Tacha was originally a dark-skinned lady while growing up. She is one of the most popular housemates of the show and many are tipping her to win the N60 million worth of prizes at the end of the show which is soon winding down. See reactions below:  Source